  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada glagol prati prefiks/afiks, često uzima formu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-ing</span>, poznatu kao gerund. Gerund je glagol koji se koristi kao imenica. Ovo pravilo je uobičajeno u mnogim engleskim frazama. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">After eating dinner, we watched a movie.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">eating</span> prati prefiks <span class=\"highlighted-text\">after</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She is interested in learning Spanish.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">learning</span> pratiš prefiks <span class=\"highlighted-text\">in</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Before going to bed, I like to read.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going</span> sledi prefiks <span class=\"highlighted-text\">before</span>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
